{"lemma":"مُسَجِّلاتٌ","slug":"مُسَجِّلاتٌ","root":"س.ج.ل","root_slug":"س-ج-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ج-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n18989"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%90%D9%91%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"registrar, notary public"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"tape recorder","examples":[{"text":"مُسَجِّل بَصَرِيّ","english":"video recorder"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of سَجَّلَ (sajjala, “to record”)."},"ipa":["/mu.sad͡ʒ.d͡ʒil/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n18989","headword_ar":"مُسْجَلٌ","root":"sjl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Allowed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made allowable, to every one;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not denied to any one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b2-  Mohammad Ibn-El-Hanafeeyeh said, in explaining the words of the Kur [lv. 60],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"halo jazaA='u A@loA_iHosaAni","text_ar":"هَلْ جَزَا=ءُ ا@لْاـِحْسَانِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_il~aA A@loA_iHosaAnu","text_ar":"اـِلَّا ا@لْاـِحْسَانُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[Shall the recompense of doing good be other than doing good?],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hiYa musojalapN lilobar~i wa AlfaAjiri","text_ar":"هِىَ مُسْجَلَةٌ لِلْبَرِّ وَ الفَاجِرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It is unrestricted in its relation to the righteous and the unrighteous:"},{"kind":"text","text":"a righteous person is not made to be conditionally intended thereby, exclusively of an unrighteous. (As, S, TA.) ―         -b3-  And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEalonaAhu wa Ald~ahoru musojalN","text_ar":"فَعَلْنَاهُ وَ الدَّهْرُ مُسْجَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We did it when fortune was unrestricted"},{"kind":"text","text":"], i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when no one feared any one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}